#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest-json.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In this example, we will create an application to manage a list of fruits."
msgstr "在这个示例中，我们将创建一个用于管理水果列表的应用程序。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest-json.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "First, let's create the `Fruit` bean as follows:"
msgstr "首先，让我们按照以下方式创建 `Fruit` Bean："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest-json.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Nothing fancy. One important thing to note is that having a default constructor is required by the JSON serialization layer."
msgstr "没什么特别的。需要注意的一点是，JSON 序列化层要求必须提供默认构造函数。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest-json.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Now, create the `org.acme.rest.json.FruitResource` class as follows:"
msgstr "现在，请按以下方式创建 `org.acme.rest.json.FruitResource` 类："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest-json.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The implementation is pretty straightforward, and you just need to define your endpoints using the Jakarta REST annotations."
msgstr "实现过程非常简单，你只需使用 Jakarta REST 注解来定义你的端点即可。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest-json.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `Fruit` objects will be automatically serialized/deserialized by https://eclipse-ee4j.github.io/jsonb-api/[JSON-B] or https://github.com/FasterXML/jackson[Jackson],\n"
"depending on the extension you chose when initializing the project."
msgstr "`Fruit` 对象将由 link:https://eclipse-ee4j.github.io/jsonb-api/[JSON-B] 或 link:https://github.com/FasterXML/jackson[Jackson] 自动进行序列化/反序列化，具体取决于您在初始化项目时选择的扩展。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/rest-json.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When a JSON extension is installed such as `quarkus-rest-jackson` or `quarkus-rest-jsonb`, Quarkus will use the `application/json` media type\n"
"by default for most return values, unless the media type is explicitly set via\n"
"`@Produces` or `@Consumes` annotations (there are some exceptions for well known types, such as `String` and `File`, which default to `text/plain` and `application/octet-stream`\n"
"respectively)."
msgstr "当安装了 JSON 扩展（例如 `quarkus-rest-jackson` 或 `quarkus-rest-jsonb` ）时， Quarkus 会默认对大多数返回值使用 `application/json` 媒体类型，除非通过 `@Produces` 或 `@Consumes` 注解显式设置了媒体类型（对于一些已知类型，如 `String` 和 `File，` 存在例外情况，它们默认分别设置为 `text/plain` 和 `application/octet-stream` ）。"

#. type: Title ==
